<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>คำทายของเพื่อนๆ</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #f8fafc; --surface: #ffffff; --text: #0f172a; --text-muted: #64748b; --border: #e2e8f0; --primary: #2563eb; }
        body { font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif; background-color: var(--bg); color: var(--text); margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .nav-link { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
        
        .match-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b, #0f172a); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; text-align: center; color: white; margin-bottom: 30px; box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1); }
        .match-header h4 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #94a3b8; font-weight: 400; }
        .match-teams { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 20px; }
        .vs-badge { background: #38bdf8; color: #0f172a; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
        
        .card { background: var(--surface); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.05); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        th, td { padding: 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
        th { background-color: var(--bg); font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .user-cell { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.05rem; }
        .user-cell img { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 2px solid var(--border); }
        .prediction-score { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: center; }
        .earned-points { color: #10b981; font-weight: 700; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="nav-link">⬅️ กลับหน้าหลักทายผล</a>
        
        <div class="match-header">
            <h4><%= match.stage_name %></h4>
            <div class="match-teams">
                <span><%= match.home_team %></span>
                <span class="vs-badge">VS</span>
                <span><%= match.away_team %></span>
            </div>
            <% if(match.status === 'FINISHED') { %>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #10b981; font-weight: bold;">ผลแข่งจริง: <%= match.home_score %> - <%= match.away_score %></p>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">👁️ ผลการทายของทุกคนในแมตช์นี้</h3>
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th width="40%">ผู้เล่น</th>
                        <th width="30%" style="text-align: center;">ทายสกอร์ไว้ว่า</th>
                        <th width="30%">คะแนนที่ได้จากคู่นี้</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <% if(predictions.length === 0) { %>
                        <tr><td colspan="3" style="text-align: center; padding: 30px; color: var(--text-muted);">ยังไม่มีผู้เล่นคนไหนทายผลคู่นี้เลย</td></tr>
                    <% } %>
                    <% predictions.forEach(p => { %>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div class="user-cell">
                                    <img src="<%= p.avatar %>" alt="avatar">
                                    <%= p.username %>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                            <td class="prediction-score">
                                <%= p.home_predict %> - <%= p.away_predict %>
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <% if(match.status === 'FINISHED') { %>
                                    <span class="earned-points">+<%= p.score_earned || 0 %> แต้ม</span>
                                <% } else { %>
                                    <span style="color: var(--text-muted);">รอแข่งจบ</span>
                                <% } %>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    <% }) %>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>